LightSpeed,Gaming,s,Reseller,Program,allows,users,to,resell,voice,servers,in,worldwide,locations,The,Reseller,Program,is,designed,for,established,businesses,with,existing,customer,bases,looking,to,add,another,value,added,service,to,their,product,offering,To,use,the,API,a,user,must,be,signed,up,as,a,reseller,The,API,can,be,used,to,control,all,of,the,voice,communication,services,and,can,be,integrated,into,a,user,s,web,site,or,application,The,API,uses,SOAP,protocol,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML